# Stats Count-Up Section — Full Extraction

---

## 1. Tech Summary

| Aspect | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Framework** | Next.js (App Router) with React 18+ |
| **Language** | TypeScript (TSX) |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS **v4** (using `@theme` block in CSS, *no* `tailwind.config.*` file) |
| **Animation library** | **`framer-motion ^12.29.0`** — only `useInView` is used (scroll-triggered visibility detection) |
| **Count-up logic** | Custom [useCountUp](file:///Users/zhengpeixian/ZPX/Work/KEA/KE_Academy/ke-academy-next/src/components/home/StatsSection.tsx#7-37) hook using `requestAnimationFrame` — *no* third-party count-up library |
| **Scroll detection** | `useInView` from `framer-motion` with `{ once: true, margin: "-100px" }` (fires once, 100 px before section enters viewport) |

