### Mount hierarchy

```
Home (page.tsx)
  └─ <StatsSection />
       └─ <Container>              ← max-w-7xl centered wrapper
            └─ grid (2-col mobile / 4-col desktop)
                 ├─ <StatItem value={700} label="Current Enrollments" color="teal"   />
                 ├─ <StatItem value={150} label="Qualified Staff"     color="green"  />
                 ├─ <StatItem value={30}  label="Courses"             color="pink"   />
                 └─ <StatItem value={20}  label="Campuses"            color="peach"  />
```

